1932;;Behind the Mask;;American;;John Francis Dillon;;Jack Holt, Boris Karloff, Constance Cummings;;drama, horror;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Behind_the_Mask_(1932_film);;A federal agent (Holt) goes undercover to infiltrate a drug smuggling operation headed by a mysterious Mr. X (Van Sloan), a criminal mastermind whose identity is unknown even to his henchmen. Mr. X is also running a bogus hospital where victims are killed on the operating table, and their coffins stuffed with narcotics. The drug-filled coffins are then buried in a cemetery.